LICENCE INFORMATION
-------------------

The Inline::SLang Perl module is released under the same terms as Perl
itself. Please see the "README" file in the Perl distribution for more
details. The Inline::SLang module is designed to be linked against
version 1.X of the S-Lang library; please note the following, taken
from the S-Lang homepage at http://www.s-lang.org/

Programs using version 1.X of the S-Lang library must be distributed
either under the terms of the GNU General Public License, or under the
terms of the Artistic License.

